{"id":123558,"type":1,"name":"射鵰英雄傳","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/74/df/123558_2H6tX.jpg","rating":{"total":45,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":1,"6":1,"7":8,"8":17,"9":10,"10":7},"score":8.2},"summary":"《射鵰英雄傳》是一部武俠小說，金庸「射鵰三部曲」之第一部，又名《大漠英雄傳》。書名《射鵰英雄傳》也因為暗合毛澤東的詞句（詩詞中有「一代天驕，成吉思汗，只識彎弓射大雕」之句），而被迫在台灣戒嚴時期改成了《大漠英雄傳》。《射鵰英雄傳》被金庸小說的讀者稱為「俠文化的歌頌」。它的發表確立了金庸「武林至尊」的地位。該小說被多次改編成同名電視連續劇、電玩遊戲。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>射雕英雄传</li><li><span>话数: </span>40回</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/16038\">金庸</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>大漠英雄傳</li><li><span>出版社: </span>明河社、遠流</li><li><span>发售日: </span>1957年</li>","collection":{"collect":59,"doing":3,"dropped":3},"tags":[{"name":"金庸","count":15},{"name":"武侠","count":13},{"name":"小说","count":9},{"name":"中国","count":2},{"name":"国产","count":2},{"name":"江湖","count":1},{"name":"NN","count":1},{"name":"国","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":16038,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/3f/9d/16038_prsn_XvIGB.jpg","name":"查良镛","desc":"作者"}],"relations":[{"id":260678,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/50/7d/260678_n20aM.jpg","title":"東邪西毒","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/260678"},{"id":215077,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/a7/e4/215077_zmXLX.jpg","title":"射雕英雄传 (2017)","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/215077"},{"id":123272,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/95/45/123272_lLwW2.jpg","title":"射鵰英雄傳 (1976)","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/123272"},{"id":123264,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b2/f1/123264_VKk4O.jpg","title":"射鵰英雄傳之鐵血丹心","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/123264"},{"id":123268,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/0b/4a/123268_rJ14r.jpg","title":"射鵰英雄傳之東邪西毒","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/123268"},{"id":123269,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/6f/da/123269_U0KKd.jpg","title":"射鵰英雄傳之華山論劍","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/123269"},{"id":123274,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/7d/f7/123274_cApjh.jpg","title":"射鵰英雄傳","type":"三次元","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/123274"},{"